.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, skateboard, bus, snowmobile, helicopter
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: tennis, rugby, rowing, sailing, ice-hockey
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
5 different pets are kept: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. the person driving the train is the person who likes red
2. the person driving the swedish is the owner of the dog
3. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is sailing
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the person who's sport is rugby
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the owner of the bird
7. the person who likes yellow is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person who's sport is rowing is in the middle
9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the cat
11. the owner of the horses is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who's sport is tennis
13. the person driving the bus is the prince-smoker
14. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Transport	|   snowmobile	|    skateboard	|    train	|    bus	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     cat	|    horse	|     bird	|     fish	|      dog	|
| Sport	|    ice-hockey	|     sailing	|     rowing	|    rugby	|      tennis	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
